extendedInfo.description: If bug exists, please tell us (E-mail), we will fix it as soon as possible.Star Wars is an American epic space opera franchise conceived by George Lucas. The first film in the franchise was originally released on May 25, 1977, under the title Star Wars, by 20th Century Fox, and became a worldwide pop culture phenomenon, followed by two sequels, released at three-year intervals. Sixteen years after the release of the trilogy's final film, the first in a new prequel trilogy of films was released, again at three-year intervals, with the final film released on May 19, 2005.The Star Wars film series has spawned other media including books, television series, video games, and comic books. These supplements to the film trilogies comprise the Star Wars Expanded Universe, and have resulted in significant development of the series' fictional universe. These media kept the franchise going in the interim between the film trilogies.In her courtesy of 300+ wallpapers and many icons for popular application and graphic user interfaces for different devices(HTC, Samsung, Motorola, etc).You can change the Wallpapers from the menu by selecting âChoose Wallpaperâ. The first five Wallpapers are stored in the application. Everyone else will be downloaded from the Internet and stored in a folder(wallpaper _duomob).This theme is compatible with Crazy Home Pro, Crazy Home Lite, ADW Launcher, Live Home, Open Home, Open Home 6, aHome, 91 Panda Home, 91 Panda Home 2.If using Crazy Home, once it is installed and running, press your Menu Key -> Crazy Menu -> Appearance -> Set Theme.If using ADW.Launcher, once it is installed and running, press your Menu Key -> More -> ADWSettings -> Themes Preferences.If using Go Launcher Ex, once it is installed and running, press your Menu Key -> Themes-> Select theme-> Apply.This application does not violate the copyright and does not claim to it.All that is in this appendix are collected from free sources.If you are the author of the material or the copyright holder for it and against its use in this, please contact me and the material will be removed or will be listed your copyright.
